name: VIP Game 20G
description: For those of lighter builds, walking-up game or desiring the faster handling characteristics of a 20 bore shotgun, the VIP Game 20 gauge cartridge will stand up to your needs. The 28 and 30 gram load in fibre wad will give you an all-round cartridge to deliver outstanding results whatever the quarry species. Superior patterning and ballistics are synonymous with the range, ensuring best in class performance.
Once you shoot with Eley VIP's nothing else is quite the same. Superior patterning and ballistics ensure the best in class performance.
